➜"迷你"金三江募资远超资产 产品价低成本高毛利率夺冠
http://www.sohu.com/a/434106205_120702	85172
<p><strong><span>中国经济网编者按</span><span>：</span></strong><span>11</span><span>月</span><span>18</span><span>日，金三江（肇庆）硅材料股份有限公司（简称“金三江”）首发过会。创业板上市委会议提出问询的主要问题有：说明牙膏用二氧化硅产品平均销售价格低于市场价格、主要原材料平均采购价格普遍高于市场价格的合理性。实际控制人占用公司资金，相关内控是否已得到改善。</span></p>
<p align="left" style="text-align: left;"><span>金三江拟在深交所创业板上市，拟发行股数不超过</span><span>3043</span><span>万股，占公司发行后总股本的比例不低于</span><span>25%</span><span>，保荐机构是中信证券。金三江拟募集资金</span><span>4.72</span><span>亿元，其中，</span><span>4.12</span><span>亿元用于二氧化硅生产基地建设项目，</span><span>6026.73</span><span>万元用于研发中心建设项目。</span></p>
<p><span>金三江专业从事沉淀法二氧化硅的研发、生产和销售。公司的控股股东是飞雪集团；共同实际控制人是任振雪与赵国法，两人系夫妻关系。金三江表示，公司</span><span>2020</span><span>年上半年收到的关联方利息收入合计</span><span>32.05</span><span>万元，是报告期内任振雪、赵国法占用公司资金按照一年期人民银行贷款基准利率</span><span>4.35%</span><span>计算的利息收入。其中，任振雪</span><span>2017</span><span>年</span><span>2</span><span>月至</span><span>2017</span><span>年</span><span>12</span><span>月拆借金额</span><span>578</span><span>万元，</span><span>2017</span><span>年</span><span>2</span><span>月至</span><span>2017</span><span>年</span><span>10</span><span>月拆借金额</span><span>300</span><span>万元，</span><span>2017</span><span>年</span><span>4</span><span>月至</span><span>2018</span><span>年</span><span>3</span><span>月拆借金额</span><span>30</span><span>万元；赵国法</span><span>2017</span><span>年</span><span>4</span><span>月至</span><span>2018</span><span>年</span><span>3</span><span>月拆借金额</span><span>30</span><span>万元。</span></p>
<p><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年、</span><span>2020</span><span>年</span><span>1-6</span><span>月，金三江现金分红分别为</span><span>2504.00</span><span>万元、</span><span>1878.00</span><span>万元、</span><span>0</span><span>元、</span><span>912.30</span><span>万元；加权平均净资产收益率分别为</span><span>33.49%</span><span>、</span><span>47.70%</span><span>、</span><span>35.35%</span><span>、</span><span>9.99%</span><span>。各期，金三江主要产品牙膏用二氧化硅（磨擦型二氧化硅、增稠型二氧化硅、综合型二氧化硅）的产能利用率分别为</span><span>82.43%</span><span>、</span><span>92.36%</span><span>、</span><span>89.00%</span><span>、</span><span>63.27%</span><span>，产销率分别为</span><span>90.89%</span><span>、</span><span>95.30%</span><span>、</span><span>90.53%</span><span>、</span><span>108.41%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年、</span><span>2020</span><span>年</span><span>1-6</span><span>月，金三江实现营业收入分别为</span><span>1.11</span><span>亿元、</span><span>1.65</span><span>亿元、</span><span>1.98</span><span>亿元、</span><span>8394.65</span><span>万元，销售商品、提供劳务收到的现金分别为</span><span>1.09</span><span>亿元、</span><span>1.60</span><span>亿元、</span><span>1.97</span><span>亿元、</span><span>1.05</span><span>亿元，销售收现比分别是</span><span>98.09%</span><span>、</span><span>97.21%</span><span>、</span><span>99.21%</span><span>、</span><span>125.09%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年、</span><span>2020</span><span>年</span><span>1-6</span><span>月，金三江实现归属于母公司所有者的净利润</span><span>2969.31</span><span>万元、</span><span>4767.49</span><span>万元、</span><span>5759.64</span><span>万元、</span><span>2376.09</span><span>万元，经营活动产生的现金流量净额分别为</span><span>2573.13</span><span>万元、</span><span>4916.33</span><span>万元、</span><span>4017.62</span><span>万元、</span><span>3654.37</span><span>万元。</span></p>
<p><span>公司</span><span>2019</span><span>年营业收入增速和净利润增速放缓，</span><span>2020</span><span>年</span><span>1-9</span><span>月营业收入降</span><span>5.65%</span><span>。</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年，公司营业收入增速分别为</span><span>48.51%</span><span>、</span><span>20.65%</span><span>，净利增速分别为</span><span>60.56%</span><span>、</span><span>20.81%</span><span>。</span><span>2020</span><span>年</span><span>1-9</span><span>月，金三江实现营业收入</span><span>1.35</span><span>亿元，同比减少</span><span>5.65%</span><span>；归属于发行人股东的净利润</span><span>4036.76</span><span>万元，同比增加</span><span>9.92%</span><span>；归属于发行人股东扣除非经常性损益后的净利润</span><span>3787.98</span><span>万元，同比增加</span><span>4.52%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>2017</span><span>年末、</span><span>2018</span><span>年末、</span><span>2019</span><span>年末、</span><span>2020</span><span>年</span><span>6</span><span>月末，金三江资产总额分别为</span><span>1.37</span><span>亿元、</span><span>1.65</span><span>亿元、</span><span>2.62</span><span>亿元、</span><span>2.67</span><span>亿元，负债合计</span><span>5883.10</span><span>万元、</span><span>5728.39</span><span>万元、</span><span>3579.21</span><span>万元、</span><span>2609.18</span><span>万元，资产负债率（母公司）</span><span>42.05%</span><span>、</span><span>33.40%</span><span>、</span><span>21.79%</span><span>、</span><span>9.97%</span><span>，资产负债率（合并报表）</span><span>42.85%</span><span>、</span><span>34.79%</span><span>、</span><span>13.67%</span><span>、</span><span>9.78%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>上述数据可见，金三江此次拟募集资金</span><span>4.72</span><span>亿元，比今年上半年末总资产高出</span><span>2.05</span><span>亿元。</span></p>
<p><span>2017</span><span>年末、</span><span>2018</span><span>年末、</span><span>2019</span><span>年末、</span><span>2020</span><span>年</span><span>6</span><span>月末，金三江货币资金余额分别为</span><span>229.21</span><span>万元、</span><span>649.70</span><span>万元、</span><span>8683.65</span><span>万元、</span><span>9677.93</span><span>万元，占流动资产的比例为</span><span>3.62%</span><span>、</span><span>7.45%</span><span>、</span><span>48.98%</span><span>、</span><span>57.59%</span><span>。</span></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
